Experience the thrill of the BMW M4 in your new tab! This Chrome extension brings the essence of this stunning sports car right to your browser.

The BMW M4 live wallpaper extension features a captivating design that highlights the sleek curves and powerful presence of this automotive icon. With a minimalist interface, you can fully appreciate the beauty of the M4 while enjoying essential browsing tools.

Navigate effortlessly with a Google search bar, access your favorite websites through customizable shortcuts, and keep track of the time with an integrated clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper showcasing the impressive BMW M4
Google Search Bar for fast web access
Customizable site shortcuts for quick navigation
Clock-Date display to stay organized

Bring the excitement of the BMW M4 to every new tab! For more unique automotive wallpapers, visit Gameograf.com and elevate your browsing experience.
